2012年2月10日，北美在线报道称“薄瓜瓜与中共元老陈云的孙女陈晓丹这对「红三代」情侣已在几个月前分手”<ref name="与中共元老陈云的孙女陈晓丹分手">{{cite web | url=http://www.naol.ca/news/world/2012/02/10-3.htm | title=红三代情侣薄瓜瓜与陈晓丹被爆分手了 | publisher=北美在线（NAOL.CA） | date=2012-02-10 | accessdate=2012-11-29 | archive-date=2013-01-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130119120043/http://naol.ca/news/world/2012/02/10-3.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 红色法拉利事件 ===
《[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]》报道，薄瓜瓜曾于2011年初某晚驾驶紅色[[法拉利|法拉利]]开车载时任美国驻华大使[[洪博培|洪博培]]先生的女儿到一家酒吧聚会<ref name="华尔街日报">{{cite news |title=Children of the Revolution |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111904491704576572552793150470.html |publisher=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]] |author=JEREMY PAGE |date=2011-11-26 |accessdate=2012-03-26 |language=en |quote=One evening early this year, a red Ferrari pulled up outside a popular bar in Beijing, and the son of one of China's top leaders stepped out, dressed in a tuxedo. Bo Guagua, 23, had driven with the daughter of the then-U.S. ambassador, Jon Huntsman, from a dinner appointment to the bar. |archive-date=2012-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323100305/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424053111904491704576572552793150470.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年2月7日[[王立军事件|王立军事件]]发生后，2012年2月10日北美在线援引澳洲传媒报道：薄瓜瓜最近向友人澄清，他早前与前美国驻华大使洪博培之女约会开的那架红色法拉利，并不是他自己的，是向朋友借来的<ref name="与中共元老陈云的孙女陈晓丹分手" />。

2012年3月，其父[[薄熙来|薄熙来]]在接受采访时否认此事，并认为这是诽谤。并且声称，自己和家人没有任何个人资产，薄瓜瓜是靠“全额奖学金”在哈佛大学读书<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.ifeng.com/mainland/special/2012lianghui/yulu/detail_2012_03/11/13110489_0.shtml |title=薄熙来：有人给我泼脏水 造谣说我儿子开红色法拉利 |publisher=[[凤凰网|凤凰网]] |date=2012-03-11 |accessdate=2012-03-26 |language=zh-hans |archive-date=2012-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314233027/http://news.ifeng.com/mainland/special/2012lianghui/yulu/detail_2012_03/11/13110489_0.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年4月24日，薄瓜瓜给哈佛大学校报《Harvard Crimson》电子邮件，声明自己从未驾驶过法拉利，也没有去过美国驻华大使洪博培官邸<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thecrimson.com/article/2012/4/24/bo-guagua-statement-to-the-crimson/ |title=The Harvard Crimson: An Exclusive Statement from Bo Guagua to The Harvard Crimson |accessdate=2012-04-28 |archive-date=2012-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120527035013/http://www.thecrimson.com/article/2012/4/24/bo-guagua-statement-to-the-crimson/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="defuse">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/26/world/asia/bo-guagua-tries-to-defuse-sports-car-scandal.html?ref=global-home# |title=Disgraced Chinese Official’s Son Tries to Defuse Sports Car Scandal |publisher=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |date=2012-04-25 |accessdate=2012-04-26 |author=ANDREW JACOBS与EDWARD WONG |language=en |archive-date=2018-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226092235/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/04/26/world/asia/bo-guagua-tries-to-defuse-sports-car-scandal.html?ref=global-home |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年4月30日，[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]記者张大卫（David Barboza）和黄安伟<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.infzm.com/content/15640 |title=外媒：北京欢迎你报道 |accessdate=2012-11-29 |archive-date=2012-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120811144722/http://www.infzm.com/content/15640 |dead-url=no }}</ref>报道，基于对洪博培女儿、薄瓜瓜以及当时共进晚餐的三人采访，表示薄瓜瓜开紅色法拉利抵大使官邸的北京传言细节不符：洪博培女儿是由聚会组织者接去晚餐<ref name="Refuted">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/05/01/world/asia/in-china-details-in-bo-guagua-episode-challenged.html |title=Details Are Refuted in Tale of Bo Guagua’s Red Ferrari |publisher=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] |date=2012-05-01 |accessdate=2012-05-01 |author=DAVID BARBOZA与EDWARD WONG |language=en |archive-date=2012-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120502030436/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/05/01/world/asia/in-china-details-in-bo-guagua-episode-challenged.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但对于薄瓜瓜与洪博培的女儿从饭店饭店聚餐处坐同一辆车来到酒吧，纽时的采访结论与华日一致。在纽时报导中薄瓜瓜及其朋友声称当时是坐由司机开的黑色奥迪；大使女儿则说其当时是坐薄瓜瓜开的红色跑车，薄开的非常快<ref name="华尔街日报" /><ref name="Refuted"/>。

《华尔街日报》后又报道薄瓜瓜曾驾驶的一辆[[保时捷|保时捷]]曾三次在[[麻薩諸塞州|麻薩諸塞州]]违章<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/chinese_news/2012/04/120427_boguagua_porsche_us.shtml |title=BBC中文网 - 两岸三地 - 薄瓜瓜驾保时捷在美三次被罚 |accessdate=2013-03-26 |archive-date=2012-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120831095021/http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/chinese_news/2012/04/120427_boguagua_porsche_us.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

